description:
A 16-episode journey through the story of The Pilgrim's Progress. Part 16 of 16. Christian  awakes on the shore, dressed in white robes. At last, he has arrived at his final destination: The Celestial City. He is greeted by the King and some other familiar faces 

A production of RevelationMedia, based on John Bunyans masterpiece, this powerful allegory  will help families face the trials and temptations of the Christian Life. RevelationMedia is committed to providing quality Christian content to the US and the ends of the earth for FREE.  Donate today to support the distribution and translation of content like The Pilgrims Progress today at www.RevelationMedia.com.

Director: Robert Fernandez
Starring: John Rhys-Davies, Ben Price,  Kristyn Getty, David Thorpe 
Executive Producer: Steve Cleary
